{"article_id":"mKtFt8M41zsrzRBa","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Nearly 13 Hours Later , Sen. Paul Ends His Filibuster ;","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Here 's The Video","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"After nearly 13 hours","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"during which he had only a few short breaks","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"while sympathetic senators took over the talking ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"Republican Sen. Rand Paul of Kentucky ended his filibuster of John Brennan 's CIA nomination early Thursday .","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"As he wrapped up the marathon talkfest ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Paul said","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"he hoped","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"he had put a spotlight on the Obama administration 's use of drone attacks","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"and would be getting a response from the White House to his call for a pledge","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"that such strikes will not be used against U.S. citizens on American soil .","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"`` I 'm hopeful","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"that we have drawn attention to this issue ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"that this issue will not fade away ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"and that the president will come up with a response , ''","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"Paul said in his closing remarks ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"as The Hill reports .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"Paul did n't threaten Sen. Strom Thurmond 's record-setting filibuster of 24 hours , 18 minutes","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"( set in 1957","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"when the South Carolina senator was a Democrat ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"as USA Today reminds us )","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"or the two other filibusters","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"that went 20+ hours .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"As Politico writes ,","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"Paul said","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"he might have tried for a record","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"if nature 's call had n't been too strong :","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"`` I would try to go another 12 hours","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"and try to break Strom Thurmond 's record ,","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"but there are some limits to filibustering","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"and I am going to have to go take care of one of those here , ''","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Courtesy of C-SPAN 's video library , we 've made a clip of the entire filibuster .","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"National Review has broken the filibuster up into highlights .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Among the moments it points to :","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"``","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"As we approached the sixth hour of the filibuster ,","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"Senator Rand Paul said","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"the president 's use of drone strikes recalled the Queen 's approach to justice in Alice in Wonderland .","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"He asked ,","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"'Has America the beautiful become Alice in Wonderland ? '","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"The senator compared the Queen 's demands for 'sentence first , verdict afterwards ' to the administration 's sentencing of terrorists to death","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"before they have been tried in court . ''","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"On Morning Edition , NPR 's Tamara Keith told host Renee Montagne","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"that Paul `` felt like this drone issue was important","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"and not getting enough attention . ...","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"He stood there ...","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"[ and ] really stayed on message . ...","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"Rand Paul got a lot of attention to the issue of drones and their potential use in America . ''","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"Paul , the son of former Rep. Ron Paul","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"( R-Texas ) ,","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"is being talked about as a potential 2016 presidential contender .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"Update at 1:45 p.m . ET .","depth":4},{"id":54,"text":"Attorney General 's Response To Paul :","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"The Justice Department just released a copy of a letter","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"sent today by Attorney Gen. Eric Holder to Sen. Paul .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"It says :","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"`` It has come to my attention that you have now asked an additional question :","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"`` Does the President have the authority","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"to use a weaponized drone","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"to kill an American","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"not engaged in combat on American soil ? ''","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"The answer to that question is no . ''","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Update at 12:25 p.m . ET .","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"NPR 's Andy Carvin Has Collected References To Things","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"Paul Mentioned During The Filibuster :","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":133,"left":68,"right":132,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":68,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":98,"right":131,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":98,"left":71,"right":97,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":70,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":70,"left":2,"right":69,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":82,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":76,"right":81,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":6,"right":75,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":75,"left":7,"right":74,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":74,"left":8,"right":73,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":73,"left":9,"right":72,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":72,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"